/**
 * How urgently a guidance update should be surfaced to the driver.
 *
 * Voice layers map this to prosody (pitch/rate) and earcons; visual
 * layers to banner styling. Ordered: `Info < Warning < Critical`.
 *
 * Derivation (single source of truth for every SDK):
 *
 * - **Critical** — restriction prohibitions: an ADR tunnel prohibition
 * ([`InstructionSeverity::for_adr_decision`] on a `Blocked` decision,
 * the hook platform layers use when `check_tunnel` fires off-route)
 * and manoeuvres crossing a **gate** (a physical barrier the vehicle
 * must not run).
 * - **Warning** — approaching a restriction or interruption of the
 * drive: toll booths and ferry boardings/landings.
 * - **Info** — every normal manoeuvre.
 *
